                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 859d.00/4</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Copenhagen</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-08T16:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 8, 1915, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>185. It is understood that Danish socialists have financed Hamilton Jackson’s
                    uprising in the Danish West Indies. The present Government sends <hi
                        rend="italic">Valkyrian</hi> in order to prevent conservative criticism that
                    it does not offer protection to the whites. Sentiment in favor of selling
                    islands to the United States growing very fast.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Egan</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
